Topic: ai

AI Agent Contract

Primary contract:
  Use Wiki Graph URIs as stable object handles.

Treat every search result as a Wiki Graph URI.

Default exploration loop:
  1. `spinedigest search <archive.sdpub> <query>`
  2. `spinedigest get <archive.sdpub> <uri>`
  3. `spinedigest related <archive.sdpub> <uri>`
  4. `spinedigest evidence <archive.sdpub> <uri>`
  5. `spinedigest pack <archive.sdpub> <uri> --budget <chars>`

Use `--type` to filter object kinds:
  entity, triple, source, summary, chunk

Use `--json` or `--jsonl` when a stable machine-readable result is needed.
